Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.62,0:00:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(狙击人妻OL由奈）\（N堕入被设计的社内羞耻)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长会议的资料拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.81,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有没有怎么样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.99,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上上周不是持田不干了吗?\N有听说好像身体不适嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听说身体怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？有听到什么就和我说....知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.25,0:05:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人清纯印象的你\N竟然穿这么下流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定都想不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只有你得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.11,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚前，不，交往前你就这么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.62,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次搞时我真的吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后换别好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说不好，是在说好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反而让我很兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一下就看得很明白了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听到下流的声音吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.78,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?....  好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里爽啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪爽啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴好爽....什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小穴好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看你的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流也翘好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.90,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我舔吗....?....舔我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我舔哪啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔我的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.67,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出下流声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.86,0:17:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.33,0:20:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋也好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.48,0:22:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽，用奶头来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.85,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.38,0:23:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我舔小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好地用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.07,0:24:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很我的老二吧！？.....喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.74,0:24:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊?.....喜欢老二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.18,0:26:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.71,0:26:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.05,0:26:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要老二吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.39,0:26:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吗?......想插
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.25,0:27:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用得好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.45,0:27:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.96,0:27:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴反应很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.47,0:28:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.98,0:28:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.40,0:29:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.64,0:30:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.14,0:30:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.31,0:31:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴爽吗?......好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.96,0:33:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老二慢地插入囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.98,0:33:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.51,0:34:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.52,0:34:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好会夹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.52,0:34:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴好会夹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.03,0:34:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整根被包裹着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.17,0:36:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?.....好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.58,0:38:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.02,0:39:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去冲澡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.71,0:43:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.78,0:44:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?没精神呢?和老公吵架了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:30.29,0:44:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，只是.....怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:36.63,0:44:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是我的错觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.30,0:44:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在换衣服时，好像有人在偷看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.15,0:44:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田好像也这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.48,0:45:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名，这得好好调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:16.50,0:45:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长，很照顾部下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.37,0:45:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天收到你的礼物，谢谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:50.04,0:45:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.54,0:45:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有收倒我的礼物吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.22,0:46:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.39,0:46:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多了，用到最后真的可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.56,0:46:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，就么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.09,0:46:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(数天后)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:52.77,0:46:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?要晚点回来啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.27,0:47:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要应酬也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:05.45,0:47:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:23.46,0:47:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.49,1:01:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:42.66,1:01:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是说要查是谁在偷看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:51.00,1:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么发现吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.00,1:02:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人一定有好好锁定目标眤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:02.84,1:02:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:08.35,1:02:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.02,1:02:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，这是你的东西哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.70,1:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就我的收藏了\N就和持田一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.22,1:02:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你老公做一样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:52.89,1:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么下流的内裤让人受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.23,1:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.41,1:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就慢慢好好感受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:47.01,1:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气，好好感受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:53.01,1:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老公也收到了我寄给他持田的礼物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.61,1:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长，你说的是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.11,1:06:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这内裤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.16,1:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:10.71,1:08:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子，真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:22.06,1:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:37.40,1:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老公可是希望外遇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:46.91,1:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我则想要收集像你样的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.42,1:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们作了个交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:03.43,1:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是秘密进行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:56.48,1:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脚真美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:11.83,1:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:15.67,1:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:19.17,1:10:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:51.04,1:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:55.54,1:10:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.88,1:11:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要脱吧！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.89,1:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名.....住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:10.72,1:11:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:15.90,1:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接来比较爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.08,1:11:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田本来是我的情妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.76,1:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:44.59,1:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把她送给你老公了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.10,1:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是以你为条件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.44,1:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.20,1:13:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.56,1:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了收藏你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:04.40,1:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是付出持田啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:11.57,1:14:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让我好好用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:17.74,1:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.42,1:14:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切也都是你造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.31,1:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:12.37,1:19:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:15.21,1:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来舔我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.71,1:19:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.22,1:19:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.56,1:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:36.68,1:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都这么含你老公的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:05.27,1:23:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我骑上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:11.44,1:23:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个....什么?没办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.95,1:23:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上司命令啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:29.63,1:23:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.48,1:23:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰放下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:30.86,1:24:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:15.13,1:26:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:46.99,1:26:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.16,1:26:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想平时一样工作就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:58.17,1:26:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:03.34,1:27:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像平时那样就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.65,1:32:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一星期后)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:36.18,1:32:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就在这里让我兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:51.52,1:32:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:57.53,1:32:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:35.19,1:35:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:41.86,1:35:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:59.11,1:37:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱了奶罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:45.82,1:37:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的手去弄小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:17.18,1:38:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己爽起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:27.19,1:38:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚开一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:40.83,1:40:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:43.66,1:40:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己来用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:49.34,1:40:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好看着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:16.76,1:42:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好着的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:22.43,1:42:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴都开了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:19.32,1:43:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:54.47,1:45:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子真好呢，让我都变这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:29.40,1:47:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:39.08,1:47:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来含莱尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:42.25,1:47:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快含老二
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:20.29,1:48:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:24.85,1:49:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手也用起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:15.40,1:50:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边搓边舔我的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:17.46,1:51:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:14.08,1:53:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手再来好好弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:32.77,1:53:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头来弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:48.11,1:53:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，就这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:59.79,1:54:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多弄一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:29.72,1:55:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:25.77,1:56:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
